<h3 id="possible-acquisition">Possible Acquisition?</h3>
<p><img src="/images/Microsoft/TikTok Logo.jpg" height="100%" /> <br />
TikTok, the most downloaded app in Q1 of 2020 was created in September 2016. Ever since its creation the app has been trending and growing its users at a unprecedent growth. However recently President Trump has stated that he is going to ban TikTok through executive action. Before President Trump announced banning TikTok there was news on Microsoft being a potential buyer.</p>
